measurements.description: One large stunning flower and one bud on one 10-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal cream overlaid charteuse, well-marked mahogany veins, mahogany areas basally; synsepal cream overlaid chartreuse, mahogany veins; petals hirsute, pleasingly twisted, chartreuse, striped and blotched mahogany; pouch light green, heavily spotted mahobany; staminode bright green overlaid mahogany; substance firm; texture glossy.
